WEBVTT

1
00:00:28.488 --> 00:00:31.199
THE GREAT WALL
HAS STOOD FOR CENTURIES

2
00:00:31.282 --> 00:00:34.160
AS ONE OF MANKIND'S
MOST ENDURING WONDERS.

3
00:00:46.631 --> 00:00:48.967
IT SPANS OVER 5500 MILES

4
00:00:49.050 --> 00:00:51.844
AND TOOK MORE THAN 1700 YEARS
TO BUILD.

5
00:00:56.266 --> 00:01:01.479
IT PROTECTED FROM MANY DANGERS.
SOME ARE KNOWN. SOME ARE LEGEND.

6
00:01:02.146 --> 00:01:06.025
THIS IS ONE OF THE LEGENDS.

7
00:02:03.583 --> 00:02:05.543
Najid. cut
the horses loose!

8
00:02:57.428 --> 00:02:59.097
We have to turn back.

9
00:02:59.263 --> 00:03:01.349
We have been riding
for six months.

10
00:03:01.474 --> 00:03:03.351
And we've lost 20 men.

11
00:03:03.476 --> 00:03:04.769
But we survived.

12
00:03:04.936 --> 00:03:06.771
Yes. By chance.

13
00:03:06.896 --> 00:03:10.191
Any one of us could
have met that same fate.

14
00:03:10.316 --> 00:03:12.318
We were the strongest.

15
00:03:12.694 --> 00:03:14.362
Remember why you're here.

16
00:03:14.487 --> 00:03:18.282
In the West. we would be enemies.
and I would have to kill you.

17
00:03:18.700 --> 00:03:20.201
At least here.
we have a common goal.

18
00:03:20.326 --> 00:03:21.452
Oh. yes.

19
00:03:21.577 --> 00:03:23.121
This black powder.

20
00:03:23.746 --> 00:03:25.623
It turns air into fire.

21
00:03:26.207 --> 00:03:28.459
And kills a dozen men
at one time.

22
00:03:28.543 --> 00:03:30.461
It is the weapon
of our dreams.

23
00:03:30.545 --> 00:03:32.004
And what if
it's just a myth?

24
00:03:32.714 --> 00:03:35.049
Men have sent word
that it's real.

25
00:03:35.133 --> 00:03:36.300
And those men are dead.

26
00:03:36.426 --> 00:03:37.802
And we are next.

27
00:03:38.344 --> 00:03:39.762
We have no maps.

28
00:03:39.846 --> 00:03:41.222
no medicine

29
00:03:41.305 --> 00:03:42.473
and no food.

30
00:03:43.015 --> 00:03:44.183
No one is going back.

31
00:03:45.143 --> 00:03:48.271
We take inventory
of what we have left

32
00:03:48.438 --> 00:03:50.523
and finish
what we started.

33
00:03:50.648 --> 00:03:52.692
There's not much here.

34
00:03:53.359 --> 00:03:54.777
The moon is strong.

35
00:03:54.861 --> 00:03:56.904
When the horses
are fresh. we move.

36
00:03:56.988 --> 00:03:58.823
- To where?
- North.

37
00:03:59.449 --> 00:04:02.493
If they keep after us.
we'll kill them in the mountains.

38
00:04:02.618 --> 00:04:03.995
The magnet.

39
00:04:06.247 --> 00:04:07.790
Too heavy.

40
00:04:07.915 --> 00:04:09.000
Useless.
I'll have it.

41
00:04:11.043 --> 00:04:12.170
It's all yours.

42
00:04:17.175 --> 00:04:21.012
<i>Amigo.</i> only you would carry
a stupid magnet through the desert.

43
00:04:21.137 --> 00:04:22.680
I can use it
to make a compass.

44
00:04:25.433 --> 00:04:27.602
Rizzetti won't make it.

45
00:04:28.352 --> 00:04:30.605
The wound is festering.

46
00:04:30.772 --> 00:04:32.190
We'll be dragging
a corpse.

47
00:04:32.273 --> 00:04:34.358
I heard that.

48
00:04:35.193 --> 00:04:37.445
He's earned the right
to die where he wants.

49
00:04:39.447 --> 00:04:40.990
I've been left
for dead twice.

50
00:04:41.574 --> 00:04:43.201
It was bad luck.
For who?

51
00:04:43.326 --> 00:04:45.036
The people who left me.

52
00:04:45.620 --> 00:04:47.038
Maybe Rizzetti's right.

53
00:05:10.895 --> 00:05:12.188
Where are they?

54
00:05:24.700 --> 00:05:25.910
Hill tribes?

55
00:05:26.619 --> 00:05:27.912
It's no man.

56
00:05:29.539 --> 00:05:30.915
Then what is it?

57
00:05:31.499 --> 00:05:34.752
Whatever it is.
it's hunting.

58
00:05:45.888 --> 00:05:47.515
What was that?
I don't know.

59
00:05:48.266 --> 00:05:49.684
I took its hand.

60
00:05:49.767 --> 00:05:52.186
- We need to move.
- Agreed.

61
00:05:52.270 --> 00:05:53.563
I'll take the hand with us.

62
00:05:53.646 --> 00:05:54.939
What the hell for?

63
00:05:55.857 --> 00:05:58.234
So someone can tell me
what I just killed.

64
00:06:14.709 --> 00:06:17.044
Persistent bastards.
aren't they?

65
00:06:17.753 --> 00:06:20.673
We'll take the rise.
make a stand there.

66
00:06:21.340 --> 00:06:24.510
What a long shitting way to go to die.

67
00:07:11.682 --> 00:07:13.184
Mother of God.

68
00:07:50.054 --> 00:07:52.890
I have no need
to go down fighting.

69
00:07:53.099 --> 00:07:54.433
Agreed.

70
00:07:55.518 --> 00:07:58.437
I say we take our chances
with the gents in front of us.

71
00:07:58.604 --> 00:08:01.148
I haven't surrendered
in a while. eh?

72
00:08:03.234 --> 00:08:05.194
It'll come back
to you.

73
00:08:12.368 --> 00:08:14.745
Follow my lead.
we'll be fine.

74
00:08:15.413 --> 00:08:16.914
Of course.
my friend.

75
00:08:17.081 --> 00:08:18.749
Where you go.
I follow.

76
00:08:18.874 --> 00:08:20.751
You're doing such
a great job already.

77
00:08:25.631 --> 00:08:27.133
All Commanders
to the Great Hall!

78
00:08:27.717 --> 00:08:30.302
All Commanders report
to the General! Make way!

79
00:08:31.595 --> 00:08:33.764
Make way!

80
00:08:43.983 --> 00:08:45.693
Commander Lin
is needed immediately!

81
00:08:45.860 --> 00:08:48.237
Calling Commander Lin!

82
00:08:49.822 --> 00:08:51.574
Commander Lin
is needed immediately!

83
00:09:02.460 --> 00:09:04.170
They know what it is.

84
00:09:04.295 --> 00:09:05.713
And they don't
look happy to see it.

85
00:09:06.297 --> 00:09:08.549
All the more reason to get the hell out of here.

86
00:09:08.632 --> 00:09:10.593
Our weapons
are on that table.

87
00:09:12.386 --> 00:09:14.180
Have you lost
your mind?

88
00:09:14.305 --> 00:09:16.682
I can take out the guards
on the perimeter with my bow.

89
00:09:16.891 --> 00:09:18.476
You cut the legs out
from under the officers.

90
00:09:18.642 --> 00:09:21.187
I must confess. this is not my favorite plan.

91
00:09:21.312 --> 00:09:23.647
Where was this found?

92
00:09:26.192 --> 00:09:27.860
You speak English.

93
00:09:28.319 --> 00:09:29.528
Fantastic.

94
00:09:32.823 --> 00:09:34.575
Where was this found?

95
00:09:35.326 --> 00:09:37.078
It wasn't found.

96
00:09:37.661 --> 00:09:38.871
It was taken.

97
00:09:38.996 --> 00:09:41.290
That thing killed three men
before we took it down.

98
00:09:41.499 --> 00:09:42.500
Where?

99
00:09:43.459 --> 00:09:44.919
Two days' ride.

100
00:09:45.086 --> 00:09:46.962
North. in the mountains.

101
00:09:48.839 --> 00:09:50.549
He says two days ride north.
in the mountains.

102
00:09:50.716 --> 00:09:52.843
They claim to have killed it.

103
00:09:53.135 --> 00:09:54.804
Two days?

104
00:09:54.887 --> 00:09:56.972
Earlier than we expected.

105
00:09:57.098 --> 00:09:58.432
Strategist Wang!

106
00:09:59.100 --> 00:10:00.976
I'm listening. General.

107
00:10:02.269 --> 00:10:04.146
The two of them killed it?

108
00:10:04.396 --> 00:10:06.649
Two of you.
you did this?

109
00:10:06.816 --> 00:10:08.609
Well...

110
00:10:08.692 --> 00:10:09.985
I killed it.

111
00:10:10.069 --> 00:10:11.487
Alone?

112
00:10:14.698 --> 00:10:16.158
He claims to have
killed it alone.

113
00:10:16.242 --> 00:10:17.493
By himself?

114
00:10:17.701 --> 00:10:18.744
Impossible.

115
00:10:20.704 --> 00:10:22.373
Tell me how.

116
00:10:23.207 --> 00:10:24.792
A swing of the sword.

117
00:10:24.875 --> 00:10:26.961
The hand.
it came away clean.

118
00:10:27.670 --> 00:10:30.005
The beast fell back
into a chasm.

119
00:10:30.548 --> 00:10:32.174
Why are you here?

120
00:10:32.258 --> 00:10:34.009
We came to trade.

121
00:10:34.093 --> 00:10:35.511
We were ambushed.

122
00:10:37.221 --> 00:10:38.222
Guards!

123
00:10:50.192 --> 00:10:51.277
You are soldiers.

124
00:10:54.738 --> 00:10:56.073
Commander Lin.

125
00:10:56.615 --> 00:10:57.616
Wait.

126
00:11:02.079 --> 00:11:03.080
Mmm.

127
00:11:07.960 --> 00:11:09.044
General.

128
00:11:09.128 --> 00:11:11.505
They claim to be traders
who were ambushed.

129
00:11:13.048 --> 00:11:15.426
These barbarians are liars.

130
00:11:15.718 --> 00:11:16.927
Perhaps not.

131
00:11:17.928 --> 00:11:19.513
They brought the claw here.

132
00:11:19.597 --> 00:11:22.099
The wound is fresh.

133
00:11:22.183 --> 00:11:24.727
There is green blood
on his sword.

134
00:11:24.852 --> 00:11:26.145
Those prove his story.

135
00:11:30.608 --> 00:11:32.443
To protect our secret...

136
00:11:32.526 --> 00:11:33.611
we must kill them.

137
00:11:33.736 --> 00:11:34.945
Eliminate the possibility
of trouble.

138
00:11:35.613 --> 00:11:36.864
I agree.

139
00:11:37.114 --> 00:11:38.115
We should kill them!

140
00:11:41.076 --> 00:11:42.161
General.

141
00:11:42.745 --> 00:11:45.539
Until we find the truth...

142
00:11:45.623 --> 00:11:47.416
I advise we keep them alive.

143
00:11:47.541 --> 00:11:48.792
Alert!

144
00:11:51.962 --> 00:11:53.923
General. signals
from the smoke towers!

145
00:11:54.173 --> 00:11:55.299
We are under attack!

146
00:11:55.466 --> 00:11:57.551
Take them to the stockade.

147
00:11:57.635 --> 00:12:00.054
All stations on full alert!

148
00:12:00.179 --> 00:12:01.805
All stations on full alert!

149
00:12:22.952 --> 00:12:24.662
Are you killing us. sister?

150
00:12:24.828 --> 00:12:26.455
Two lost travelers?

151
00:12:28.082 --> 00:12:29.750
What's happening here?

152
00:12:29.875 --> 00:12:31.543
Is this bitch
going to kill us?

153
00:12:31.710 --> 00:12:33.170
I think she'd like that.

154
00:12:34.880 --> 00:12:38.509
If it is death. my dear.
we need time to pray.

155
00:12:39.176 --> 00:12:40.302
I'm trying here.

156
00:12:42.054 --> 00:12:44.848
Sister. I know a siege
when I see one.

157
00:12:45.516 --> 00:12:48.018
What comes at you so hard
you need a wall like this?

158
00:12:48.185 --> 00:12:49.979
What the hell
did we kill out there?

159
00:12:50.062 --> 00:12:51.563
Tao Tei.

160
00:12:52.273 --> 00:12:54.566
You killed
a Tao Tei scout.

161
00:12:54.692 --> 00:12:56.026
You killed it alone.

162
00:12:56.694 --> 00:12:57.861
You're correct.

163
00:12:57.987 --> 00:12:59.363
We are under siege.

164
00:13:00.072 --> 00:13:02.741
But we did not expect
the attack for another nine days.

165
00:13:02.908 --> 00:13:05.119
- Attack?
- Tao Tei.

166
00:13:05.703 --> 00:13:07.496
What the hell
is a Tao Tei?

167
00:13:07.621 --> 00:13:09.873
Many things about your story have importance.

168
00:13:10.416 --> 00:13:11.834
You are not to die today.

169
00:13:17.715 --> 00:13:20.384
- Hurry!
- I'm sorry. sir...

170
00:13:20.551 --> 00:13:22.594
- I cannot find the key.
- Forget it!

171
00:13:22.720 --> 00:13:25.639
Bring them to the Wall.
Keep an eye on them!

172
00:13:32.896 --> 00:13:34.064
General.

173
00:13:34.231 --> 00:13:35.566
It's finally happening.

174
00:13:36.400 --> 00:13:37.651
Yes.

175
00:13:38.610 --> 00:13:41.488
Sixty years preparing
for this moment.

176
00:15:56.665 --> 00:15:58.876
The black are
the foot soldiers.

177
00:15:59.209 --> 00:16:00.210
And the red?

178
00:16:00.377 --> 00:16:01.503
Those are the archers.

179
00:16:18.228 --> 00:16:19.980
And the blue?

180
00:16:20.147 --> 00:16:21.565
They're all women.

181
00:16:21.732 --> 00:16:22.900
What the hell
do they do?

182
00:16:37.331 --> 00:16:39.082
Look at this army.

183
00:16:40.167 --> 00:16:41.919
Have you ever seen
anything like this?

184
00:16:42.002 --> 00:16:43.587
Incredible.

185
00:17:03.607 --> 00:17:05.400
They look nervous.

186
00:17:06.443 --> 00:17:09.279
It's a big wall
to be so nervous.

187
00:17:27.589 --> 00:17:29.216
Do you hear it?

188
00:17:36.598 --> 00:17:37.558
Long distance weapons!

189
00:17:37.641 --> 00:17:39.476
Yes! Drums signal
long distance weapons!

190
00:18:34.906 --> 00:18:36.199
Aim for the eyes!

191
00:18:36.283 --> 00:18:37.618
Aim for the eyes!

192
00:18:57.804 --> 00:18:59.056
Crane Corps attack!

193
00:20:02.202 --> 00:20:04.454
William. over there.

194
00:20:06.123 --> 00:20:07.958
Why isn't he tied up?

195
00:20:09.668 --> 00:20:10.919
There's our escape.

196
00:20:32.315 --> 00:20:35.026
General. There's the Queen!
She commands them!

197
00:20:35.652 --> 00:20:36.653
Attack the Queen!

198
00:21:14.691 --> 00:21:15.817
Close combat!

199
00:21:15.901 --> 00:21:17.027
Yes! Close combat!

200
00:21:17.110 --> 00:21:18.737
Drums signal close combat!

201
00:21:41.551 --> 00:21:43.011
We need to move!

202
00:21:43.094 --> 00:21:44.721
We need to move
or we die!

203
00:22:02.739 --> 00:22:03.740
Go. go!

204
00:22:05.450 --> 00:22:06.576
Go and fight!

205
00:22:12.958 --> 00:22:14.751
Cut me loose!

206
00:22:18.588 --> 00:22:19.589
Fight or run?

207
00:22:19.673 --> 00:22:20.674
Run where?

208
00:22:26.096 --> 00:22:28.265
Aim for the eyes!

209
00:23:07.637 --> 00:23:08.680
William!

210
00:23:35.332 --> 00:23:37.125
Hey! Bitch!

211
00:23:53.058 --> 00:23:54.351
William.

212
00:23:54.476 --> 00:23:55.852
I need a shot.

213
00:24:43.400 --> 00:24:45.735
What god made
those things?

214
00:24:46.736 --> 00:24:48.571
None that we know.

215
00:25:06.548 --> 00:25:08.258
Think they'll
hang us now?

216
00:25:08.425 --> 00:25:10.427
I could use the rest.

217
00:25:35.702 --> 00:25:37.871
You fought well today.

218
00:25:38.079 --> 00:25:39.789
You've earned
General Shao's praise.

219
00:25:39.914 --> 00:25:41.458
Will they come back?

220
00:25:41.583 --> 00:25:42.584
Yes.

221
00:25:43.168 --> 00:25:45.712
All we can do
is prepare.

222
00:25:46.963 --> 00:25:48.089
Take them to the barracks.

223
00:25:48.173 --> 00:25:49.758
They need rest.

224
00:25:49.883 --> 00:25:50.884
Yes!

225
00:26:19.079 --> 00:26:20.747
Thank you for saving my life.

226
00:26:44.479 --> 00:26:46.064
Commander Lin.

227
00:26:47.315 --> 00:26:49.609
You grew up
in the Nameless Order.

228
00:26:49.901 --> 00:26:52.487
I've taught you many things...

229
00:26:52.904 --> 00:26:55.115
and you have been learning...

230
00:26:55.865 --> 00:26:58.243
but they have
been learning also.

231
00:26:58.910 --> 00:27:01.371
Strategist Wang warned
they are evolving.

232
00:27:02.372 --> 00:27:04.499
No one listened.

233
00:27:05.208 --> 00:27:06.835
The enemies
we're facing today...

234
00:27:07.043 --> 00:27:09.546
are more intelligent
than sixty years ago.

235
00:27:12.382 --> 00:27:13.883
Watch the foreigners closely.

236
00:27:14.050 --> 00:27:15.677
They can never leave.

237
00:27:15.844 --> 00:27:17.595
We must protect
the secrets of the Wall.

238
00:27:17.720 --> 00:27:18.721
Yes. sir!

239
00:27:20.306 --> 00:27:21.975
Who are you?

240
00:27:27.564 --> 00:27:29.065
Easy.

241
00:27:31.985 --> 00:27:33.945
I'm Ballard. Hmm?

242
00:27:35.113 --> 00:27:36.239
William.

243
00:27:37.115 --> 00:27:38.533
This is Tovar.

244
00:27:39.617 --> 00:27:41.411
What are you doing here?

245
00:27:42.537 --> 00:27:44.581
We came looking
for black powder.

246
00:27:44.664 --> 00:27:46.916
I bet you did.

247
00:27:47.000 --> 00:27:49.752
I came with mercenaries
for the same thing.

248
00:27:49.836 --> 00:27:51.421
Twenty-five years ago.

249
00:27:52.255 --> 00:27:53.423
And did you find it?

250
00:27:53.590 --> 00:27:56.718
Finding it and leaving with it
alive are two different things.

251
00:28:00.096 --> 00:28:03.683
You saved the west turret.
That was extremely diplomatic.

252
00:28:03.766 --> 00:28:05.768
We weren't
being diplomatic.

253
00:28:05.852 --> 00:28:07.562
We were trying
to stay alive.

254
00:28:10.190 --> 00:28:12.817
You smell like animals.
Thank you.

255
00:28:18.364 --> 00:28:19.699
Clean up

256
00:28:20.575 --> 00:28:22.368
and they'll feed you.

257
00:28:24.454 --> 00:28:26.581
He knows where the powder is.

258
00:28:28.166 --> 00:28:29.834
Then why is he
still here?

259
00:28:30.627 --> 00:28:32.128
He needs help
getting out?

260
00:28:32.754 --> 00:28:33.755
Right.

261
00:28:34.756 --> 00:28:36.466
We play our part.

262
00:28:36.591 --> 00:28:39.552
take the powder
and go home.

263
00:28:40.887 --> 00:28:42.430
I didn't sign up for this.

264
00:28:42.555 --> 00:28:43.598
Which part?

265
00:28:44.807 --> 00:28:47.477
Well. all of it.
But mostly the monsters.

266
00:28:48.478 --> 00:28:49.812
There's a lot of them.

267
00:28:53.191 --> 00:28:55.235
We really do smell.

268
00:29:27.517 --> 00:29:30.436
General Shao welcomes you as honored guests

269
00:29:30.561 --> 00:29:34.732
of the Nameless Order and thanks
you for your skill and courage.

270
00:29:37.151 --> 00:29:40.405
We are honored
to be honored.

271
00:29:42.699 --> 00:29:44.200
Is that the best
you've got?

272
00:29:48.204 --> 00:29:49.330
General.

273
00:29:51.874 --> 00:29:53.626
I couldn't help wondering...

274
00:29:53.751 --> 00:29:56.254
why would such
an accomplished archer...

275
00:29:56.379 --> 00:29:58.881
use such a primitive bow.

276
00:30:01.342 --> 00:30:03.052
Commander Chen thinks your bow

277
00:30:03.136 --> 00:30:04.887
is not worthy
of your skill.

278
00:30:05.513 --> 00:30:07.807
Tell him there's no better weapon here.

279
00:30:07.890 --> 00:30:11.728
He claims his weapon
is second to none.

280
00:30:15.189 --> 00:30:16.983
Let him show us.

281
00:30:17.066 --> 00:30:19.152
Give him some space!

282
00:30:25.825 --> 00:30:27.535
They wish to see you shoot.

283
00:30:27.702 --> 00:30:29.078
In here?

284
00:30:29.162 --> 00:30:31.706
Unless he's afraid.

285
00:30:31.998 --> 00:30:33.082
It's a large audience.

286
00:30:33.249 --> 00:30:34.375
What was that?

287
00:30:34.500 --> 00:30:35.710
He thinks you have fear.

288
00:30:36.878 --> 00:30:38.546
Too many people.

289
00:30:41.841 --> 00:30:43.134
Get one of the cups.

290
00:30:43.259 --> 00:30:44.552
Now?
Get one of the cups.

291
00:30:44.635 --> 00:30:45.636
I want to eat.

292
00:30:53.686 --> 00:30:54.729
You remember
how to do this?

293
00:30:54.771 --> 00:30:57.023
Last time didn't go so good.
We were drunk.

294
00:30:57.774 --> 00:30:58.816
How high?

295
00:30:58.983 --> 00:31:01.778
Ten yards.
Six hands to the right.

296
00:31:01.903 --> 00:31:03.071
Turn around.

297
00:31:03.237 --> 00:31:04.489
No. I'll do it this way.

298
00:31:05.073 --> 00:31:06.532
On my count.
<i>Amigo...</i>

299
00:31:06.699 --> 00:31:08.201
One.

300
00:31:08.284 --> 00:31:09.285
Two.

301
00:31:10.453 --> 00:31:11.621
Three.

302
00:31:13.122 --> 00:31:14.749
Pull.

303
00:31:50.034 --> 00:31:51.661
Good luck with that.

304
00:31:51.828 --> 00:31:53.496
I want food.

305
00:31:53.621 --> 00:31:55.081
Who taught
you English?

306
00:31:55.665 --> 00:31:56.707
Sir Ballard.

307
00:31:58.418 --> 00:32:00.169
English and Latin.

308
00:32:01.129 --> 00:32:03.339
Heard he's been here
for 25 years.

309
00:32:03.464 --> 00:32:05.508
You won't
let him leave.

310
00:32:05.842 --> 00:32:07.343
He must stay here.

311
00:32:08.010 --> 00:32:09.178
What about us?

312
00:32:12.265 --> 00:32:13.766
Pace yourself.

313
00:32:13.850 --> 00:32:15.351
The meals
are regular here.

314
00:32:15.977 --> 00:32:17.854
I hope not
to stay that long.

315
00:32:18.020 --> 00:32:19.439
I like your thinking.

316
00:32:19.522 --> 00:32:22.358
but I suggest you keep
your plans private.

317
00:32:22.442 --> 00:32:24.360
You aren't
the first Westerners

318
00:32:24.444 --> 00:32:26.362
to come here looking
for black powder.

319
00:32:27.238 --> 00:32:30.700
We'll discuss it tonight.
Bring your partner.

320
00:32:30.825 --> 00:32:32.285
How long
have you been here?

321
00:32:32.410 --> 00:32:33.453
Always.

322
00:32:33.578 --> 00:32:36.664
I was not five years old
when I came here.

323
00:32:36.831 --> 00:32:38.916
I have no other family.

324
00:32:39.041 --> 00:32:40.751
We're the same.

325
00:32:40.835 --> 00:32:43.796
I was given to an army
before I can remember.

326
00:32:43.880 --> 00:32:45.173
As a soldier?

327
00:32:45.256 --> 00:32:48.050
Worse.
As a gleaner.

328
00:32:48.176 --> 00:32:51.053
Packs of children. we'd clean the battlefields.

329
00:32:51.137 --> 00:32:53.222
After. when the
fighting's over.

330
00:32:53.306 --> 00:32:56.601
I became a page.
a pikeman's boy...

331
00:32:56.726 --> 00:32:58.644
For your country?

332
00:32:58.728 --> 00:33:01.397
No. I fought for food.

333
00:33:02.356 --> 00:33:03.941
You fight to eat.

334
00:33:04.609 --> 00:33:06.527
You live long enough.
you fight for money.

335
00:33:07.445 --> 00:33:09.822
How many flags
do you fight for?

336
00:33:11.199 --> 00:33:12.867
I don't know.

337
00:33:14.785 --> 00:33:17.288
I fought for Harold
against the Danes.

338
00:33:17.413 --> 00:33:20.750
I saved a Duke's life.
I fought for him until he died.

339
00:33:21.292 --> 00:33:23.920
Fought for Spain
against the Franks.

340
00:33:24.253 --> 00:33:25.922
Fought for the Franks
against Boulogne.

341
00:33:26.047 --> 00:33:27.798
I fought for the Pope.

342
00:33:29.842 --> 00:33:31.761
Many flags.

343
00:33:35.056 --> 00:33:37.099
We are not the same.

344
00:33:43.564 --> 00:33:46.776
Meet me on the Wall.
I have something to show you.

345
00:33:49.946 --> 00:33:52.615
He should be
careful with her.

346
00:33:52.698 --> 00:33:54.283
She's very powerful here.

347
00:33:54.408 --> 00:33:56.827
Then it is a fair contest.

348
00:34:06.337 --> 00:34:07.463
Come.

349
00:34:19.892 --> 00:34:21.894
Hmm.
You wish to try?

350
00:34:26.691 --> 00:34:28.609
Men are too heavy.
Do you think we can pull him up?

351
00:34:31.153 --> 00:34:33.823
She says men
have so much to teach us.

352
00:34:40.496 --> 00:34:42.164
I don't think
that's what she said.

353
00:34:42.707 --> 00:34:44.292
You know what I think?

354
00:34:45.251 --> 00:34:46.377
I think you're afraid.

355
00:34:48.963 --> 00:34:50.840
You said that
this morning.

356
00:34:51.090 --> 00:34:52.091
And yet.

357
00:34:53.843 --> 00:34:55.678
here I am.
Yes.

358
00:34:56.554 --> 00:34:57.972
Here you are.

359
00:35:13.779 --> 00:35:16.657
Will you jump?
Or not?

360
00:35:19.619 --> 00:35:21.537
These men know
what they're doing?

361
00:35:21.662 --> 00:35:22.705
Wrong question.

362
00:35:26.751 --> 00:35:29.670
Whether or not
the cable is attached.

363
00:35:30.379 --> 00:35:32.798
that is the question.

364
00:35:34.759 --> 00:35:35.968
And the answer?

365
00:35:36.052 --> 00:35:37.219
Trust.

366
00:35:39.013 --> 00:35:40.389
<i>Xin ren.</i>

367
00:35:41.766 --> 00:35:45.144
<i>Xin ren</i> means trust.
To have faith.

368
00:35:46.228 --> 00:35:48.773
Here. in this army.

369
00:35:49.440 --> 00:35:52.068
we fight for more
than food or money.

370
00:35:52.443 --> 00:35:54.612
We give our lives
to something more.

371
00:35:56.530 --> 00:35:58.908
<i>Xin ren</i> is our flag.

372
00:35:59.450 --> 00:36:01.285
Trust in each other.

373
00:36:01.869 --> 00:36:05.414
In all ways.
at all times.

374
00:36:19.595 --> 00:36:22.181
Well. that's all well and good.
but I'm not jumping.

375
00:36:22.264 --> 00:36:25.601
I'm alive today
because I trust no one.

376
00:36:26.769 --> 00:36:28.938
A man must learn to trust

377
00:36:29.105 --> 00:36:31.482
before he can be trusted.

378
00:36:31.607 --> 00:36:33.567
Then you were right.

379
00:36:34.276 --> 00:36:36.070
We're not the same.

380
00:36:42.118 --> 00:36:44.203
Stay vigilant!
The next attack is coming.

381
00:36:49.458 --> 00:36:50.918
My God!

382
00:36:52.628 --> 00:36:54.338
A taste. a glimpse.

383
00:36:54.463 --> 00:36:59.260
A few pilfered grains from Strategist
Wang's supply of black powder.

384
00:37:00.636 --> 00:37:04.807
He's mastered
the transmutation of these elements.

385
00:37:04.974 --> 00:37:06.267
People speak
of a weapon.

386
00:37:06.434 --> 00:37:08.144
There are many
weapons here.

387
00:37:08.310 --> 00:37:09.603
Why have we
not seen them?

388
00:37:09.687 --> 00:37:12.898
There are many
things you have not seen.

389
00:37:12.982 --> 00:37:16.360
And many things you should
pray will not be needed

390
00:37:16.527 --> 00:37:18.904
before the siege
is through.

391
00:37:21.365 --> 00:37:23.993
The Tao Tei will return.

392
00:37:24.452 --> 00:37:26.537
When the drums
call to battle.

393
00:37:27.496 --> 00:37:31.125
the guards leave their posts and
take their positions on the Wall.

394
00:37:31.292 --> 00:37:33.836
That is our moment.

395
00:37:34.628 --> 00:37:36.213
We want to be
riding away

396
00:37:36.839 --> 00:37:38.674
as the battle rages.

397
00:37:40.843 --> 00:37:43.888
And the armory doors?
You have keys?

398
00:37:44.013 --> 00:37:45.806
I have black powder.

399
00:37:45.890 --> 00:37:47.850
Enough for
several doors.

400
00:37:48.434 --> 00:37:49.852
He brings us in.
We get us out.

401
00:37:51.145 --> 00:37:52.605
Strategist Wang
requests your presence.

402
00:37:55.399 --> 00:37:58.861
As you fought.
where was this stone?

403
00:37:59.403 --> 00:38:01.363
In my bag.

404
00:38:03.365 --> 00:38:05.242
Its unseen force
is powerful.

405
00:38:05.785 --> 00:38:08.704
I believe this strange stone could help us.

406
00:38:10.539 --> 00:38:12.500
We try everything.

407
00:38:13.626 --> 00:38:15.878
Where are the
Tao Tei now?

408
00:38:16.003 --> 00:38:18.422
The mountains. regrouping.

409
00:38:19.548 --> 00:38:21.675
Where do they
come from?

410
00:38:22.218 --> 00:38:24.386
About 20 centuries ago.

411
00:38:24.929 --> 00:38:29.308
there was an emperor whose greed
brought deep suffering to all of China.

412
00:38:29.433 --> 00:38:32.686
<i>The heavens sent the meteor
that struck Gouwu Mountain.</i>

413
00:38:32.853 --> 00:38:36.106
<i>turning it green
and releasing the Tao Tei.</i>

414
00:38:36.273 --> 00:38:40.194
<i>From that day on. the Tao Tei rise every 60 years</i>

415
00:38:40.361 --> 00:38:43.113
<i>to scourge
the north of China.</i>

416
00:38:43.280 --> 00:38:48.911
<i>They come to remind us of what
happens when greed is unchecked.</i>

417
00:38:49.078 --> 00:38:52.581
<i>They eat anything.
alive or dead.</i>

418
00:38:52.748 --> 00:38:54.875
<i>and take food
to their queen.</i>

419
00:38:55.042 --> 00:38:58.254
<i>She depends on her soldiers to feed her.</i>

420
00:38:58.420 --> 00:39:03.133
<i>Only with the food they
provide is she able to multiply.</i>

421
00:39:05.219 --> 00:39:10.474
<i>The capital. and its two million
people. is only 800 li away.</i>

422
00:39:11.392 --> 00:39:14.311
<i>If the Tao Tei ever had
that much nourishment.</i>

423
00:39:14.478 --> 00:39:17.773
no corner of the world
would be safe.

424
00:39:18.440 --> 00:39:19.775
You can't hunt them?

425
00:39:19.900 --> 00:39:21.151
Men try.

426
00:39:21.610 --> 00:39:22.653
They disappear.

427
00:39:23.279 --> 00:39:24.363
We never find
their bones.

428
00:39:25.531 --> 00:39:30.035
Troops unaccounted for
at the West Tower!

429
00:39:47.636 --> 00:39:49.763
Why did they leave the bodies?

430
00:39:51.599 --> 00:39:52.641
Dismount!

431
00:39:54.768 --> 00:39:55.978
Formation!

432
00:40:24.214 --> 00:40:25.215
Advance!

433
00:41:25.567 --> 00:41:27.194
Stop.

434
00:41:35.411 --> 00:41:36.662
Commander Lin.

435
00:41:38.288 --> 00:41:39.289
General...

436
00:41:41.083 --> 00:41:43.293
They led us into a trap.

437
00:41:43.836 --> 00:41:46.213
We underestimated their intelligence.

438
00:42:00.436 --> 00:42:02.271
The Nameless Order...

439
00:42:04.273 --> 00:42:05.941
is yours to command.

440
00:42:06.233 --> 00:42:07.234
General...

441
00:42:08.110 --> 00:42:10.571
Commanders.
this is my final order...

442
00:42:13.615 --> 00:42:15.617
...from this day forward...

443
00:42:16.160 --> 00:42:21.123
Commander Lin will lead you.

444
00:42:23.584 --> 00:42:25.294
The soldiers of
the Nameless Order...

445
00:42:25.461 --> 00:42:26.879
will stand firm.

446
00:42:27.463 --> 00:42:28.630
The Wall must not fall!

447
00:42:28.714 --> 00:42:30.632
We will defeat the Tao Tei!

448
00:42:31.175 --> 00:42:33.260
Rest in peace.

449
00:42:33.343 --> 00:42:34.720
Rest in peace!

450
00:44:14.528 --> 00:44:16.155
This is envoy
Shen from the palace.

451
00:44:16.280 --> 00:44:19.825
He has brought important records
to help with the coming battle.

452
00:44:21.785 --> 00:44:23.787
This is a 900-year-old
battle report.

453
00:44:23.996 --> 00:44:26.415
A 900-year-old battle report.

454
00:44:26.915 --> 00:44:29.501
At the Hansha gates.

455
00:44:29.626 --> 00:44:32.671
three beasts
mounted the Wall.

456
00:44:32.880 --> 00:44:36.592
They killed many men
as they went forward.

457
00:44:36.758 --> 00:44:40.345
Then. by the grace
of the ancient gods.

458
00:44:40.512 --> 00:44:42.764
the beasts stopped...

459
00:44:45.684 --> 00:44:48.854
...and sat peacefully as we slaughtered them.

460
00:44:48.937 --> 00:44:52.024
There was a magnet on site
just like this one.

461
00:44:52.232 --> 00:44:56.612
At the Hansha Gate.
was a magnet just like this one.

462
00:44:56.695 --> 00:45:01.408
I believe that magnet was
the reason that two of you Westerners

463
00:45:01.491 --> 00:45:03.577
killed the Tao Tei
so easily.

464
00:45:04.453 --> 00:45:07.998
I believe the magnet
makes the Tao Tei deaf.

465
00:45:08.624 --> 00:45:11.543
Without instruction.
they fall still.

466
00:45:14.338 --> 00:45:15.714
How to prove it?

467
00:45:15.923 --> 00:45:17.049
How can we be sure?

468
00:45:18.800 --> 00:45:19.885
Why not try it?

469
00:45:21.428 --> 00:45:22.638
Capture a Tao Tei.

470
00:45:22.804 --> 00:45:23.889
See if it works.

471
00:45:23.972 --> 00:45:25.057
He wants to try.

472
00:45:25.140 --> 00:45:26.475
He wants to catch one.

473
00:45:26.642 --> 00:45:27.643
{\an8}How?

474
00:45:27.768 --> 00:45:29.770
No net is strong enough.

475
00:45:29.895 --> 00:45:32.064
Hunt them.
Like a whale.

476
00:45:32.648 --> 00:45:34.233
You know what that is.

477
00:45:34.316 --> 00:45:35.359
Uh... A water beast.

478
00:45:35.984 --> 00:45:39.154
Hundred times
the size of a Tao Tei.

479
00:45:39.238 --> 00:45:42.074
A spear that grabs. Hook the bone. Pull them up.

480
00:45:43.325 --> 00:45:44.826
Use a spear. hook them.

481
00:45:44.952 --> 00:45:46.536
So we can catch them.

482
00:45:47.871 --> 00:45:49.748
I've seen it done in Spain.

483
00:45:49.831 --> 00:45:53.543
He claims to have
seen it done in Spain.

484
00:45:54.628 --> 00:45:56.672
What the hell
are you doing?

485
00:45:56.838 --> 00:45:58.382
We need to be free
when the attack comes.

486
00:45:58.465 --> 00:45:59.883
How many chances do you think we will get?

487
00:46:02.761 --> 00:46:06.265
Be injured. Be missing. Be a coward.

488
00:46:06.348 --> 00:46:07.975
Get out of this.

489
00:46:09.226 --> 00:46:10.519
We did enough.

490
00:46:20.529 --> 00:46:21.863
The mixture must be strong...

491
00:46:22.072 --> 00:46:23.740
...to put the creatures
to sleep.

492
00:46:29.705 --> 00:46:30.706
Spread it on evenly.

493
00:46:30.872 --> 00:46:31.915
Yes. Commander!

494
00:47:07.784 --> 00:47:09.077
Snap out of it!

495
00:47:27.429 --> 00:47:28.388
Useless idiot!

496
00:47:28.472 --> 00:47:29.723
Report to the kitchen
where you belong!

497
00:47:29.848 --> 00:47:31.433
- Yes. Commander.
- Go!

498
00:48:03.965 --> 00:48:04.966
He'll be here.

499
00:48:05.050 --> 00:48:07.219
When?
When it's over?

500
00:48:07.302 --> 00:48:09.054
We start
and he will find us.

501
00:48:09.137 --> 00:48:10.180
Start?

502
00:48:10.305 --> 00:48:11.973
We're jumping
off a cliff here.

503
00:48:12.641 --> 00:48:15.977
I have everything.
Powder. tools. maps.

504
00:48:16.103 --> 00:48:18.146
It's all hidden and arranged along the route.

505
00:48:18.313 --> 00:48:19.564
Once we start.

506
00:48:19.648 --> 00:48:22.192
there's no going back.

507
00:49:08.572 --> 00:49:10.031
Death Squad ready!

508
00:49:15.328 --> 00:49:16.329
Blades ready!

509
00:49:22.878 --> 00:49:24.504
Blades forward!

510
00:49:26.590 --> 00:49:27.591
Attack!

511
00:49:33.930 --> 00:49:34.931
Left!

512
00:49:35.348 --> 00:49:36.850
Right!

513
00:50:06.505 --> 00:50:08.340
I'll find him.
Forget him.

514
00:50:08.507 --> 00:50:11.218
He'd rather die trying to impress the new general

515
00:50:11.343 --> 00:50:16.014
than grab the key to every counting
room and brothel in the world.

516
00:50:16.681 --> 00:50:18.725
Good God. man.
The time is now!

517
00:50:18.808 --> 00:50:20.519
I can't go
without him.

518
00:50:20.644 --> 00:50:22.020
More the spoils for us!

519
00:50:22.103 --> 00:50:24.105
We need his bow!

520
00:50:27.609 --> 00:50:28.652
Harpoons!

521
00:50:28.777 --> 00:50:30.278
Harpoons. now!

522
00:50:35.659 --> 00:50:36.743
Fire!

523
00:51:17.784 --> 00:51:19.035
- There!
- Move!

524
00:51:19.578 --> 00:51:20.912
It's the last one!

525
00:51:46.521 --> 00:51:47.606
Pull!

526
00:51:47.772 --> 00:51:48.857
No. stop!

527
00:51:48.982 --> 00:51:49.983
Hold!

528
00:51:50.150 --> 00:51:51.401
There's too much tension.

529
00:51:51.526 --> 00:51:52.944
Chain will break.

530
00:51:53.028 --> 00:51:54.613
That way. That way.

531
00:51:54.696 --> 00:51:55.947
Let him run!

532
00:51:59.868 --> 00:52:01.369
Stop! Stop!

533
00:52:01.494 --> 00:52:03.872
We need longer for the sleeping potion to work.

534
00:52:08.501 --> 00:52:09.544
That way. That way.

535
00:52:11.046 --> 00:52:13.131
We need to isolate it.
Separate it from the others.

536
00:52:14.257 --> 00:52:15.258
Ring of fire!

537
00:52:31.691 --> 00:52:33.943
The chain won't hold much longer!

538
00:52:35.320 --> 00:52:36.571
We're losing it!

539
00:52:45.080 --> 00:52:46.122
William. wait.

540
00:52:46.206 --> 00:52:48.124
- Screaming arrows!
- Yes! Screaming arrows!

541
00:52:49.918 --> 00:52:53.088
These arrows
will scream as the Tao Tei run.

542
00:52:54.673 --> 00:52:55.757
Aim for the sound.

543
00:53:07.310 --> 00:53:08.770
Aim inside the circle.

544
00:53:08.937 --> 00:53:11.106
Blanket the whole area.

545
00:53:15.443 --> 00:53:16.444
Fire!

546
00:53:57.527 --> 00:53:58.695
Pull!

547
00:54:20.633 --> 00:54:23.386
I'm only saving
you so I can kill you myself.

548
00:54:25.847 --> 00:54:27.182
Grab an ax.
we're fighting blind.

549
00:54:36.775 --> 00:54:38.860
Not yet.
I know what to do!

550
00:55:09.140 --> 00:55:10.141
The fire's not
holding them back.

551
00:55:11.059 --> 00:55:12.352
Die well. brother.

552
00:55:19.442 --> 00:55:20.610
What the hell
are you doing?

553
00:55:20.735 --> 00:55:21.903
She's listening.

554
00:55:24.405 --> 00:55:26.407
Prepare black powder weapons!

555
00:55:26.741 --> 00:55:28.576
Prepare black powder weapons!

556
00:55:35.333 --> 00:55:36.417
Prepare to light the fuses!

557
00:57:03.296 --> 00:57:04.464
Did it work?

558
00:57:04.547 --> 00:57:07.175
Yes. The beast
was captured.

559
00:57:08.551 --> 00:57:10.178
My friend...

560
00:57:10.470 --> 00:57:12.138
He was unharmed.

561
00:57:22.690 --> 00:57:25.193
Why did you go
over the Wall?

562
00:57:30.198 --> 00:57:31.532
Trust.

563
00:57:33.242 --> 00:57:34.869
Did I say it right?

564
00:57:38.915 --> 00:57:40.166
Thank you.

565
00:57:46.839 --> 00:57:48.424
Black powder.

566
00:57:50.093 --> 00:57:52.220
It is a terrible weapon.

567
00:57:53.388 --> 00:57:56.849
It would be better if you had never seen it.

568
00:58:01.354 --> 00:58:04.315
I know very little
of the outside world.

569
00:58:05.108 --> 00:58:06.484
But it seems to me.

570
00:58:06.567 --> 00:58:10.029
the greed of men is not that
different from the Tao Tei.

571
00:58:11.072 --> 00:58:12.573
Is that true?

572
00:58:13.866 --> 00:58:16.494
The strong take
what they want.

573
00:58:27.463 --> 00:58:29.924
Forget what you have seen.

574
00:59:18.973 --> 00:59:20.141
Excellent!

575
00:59:20.641 --> 00:59:22.268
Send it to the capital
immediately.

576
00:59:22.351 --> 00:59:24.937
No!
We need to study it here.

577
00:59:25.146 --> 00:59:27.648
If a Tao Tei is captured alive.
it must be sent to the Emperor.

578
00:59:27.732 --> 00:59:31.277
This is an Imperial Order.

579
00:59:52.340 --> 00:59:53.382
Hmm?

580
00:59:54.425 --> 00:59:56.344
You're much
braver than they think.

581
01:00:25.039 --> 01:00:26.582
You wounded?

582
01:00:29.418 --> 01:00:31.003
I was looking for you.

583
01:00:31.921 --> 01:00:33.089
To say thank you.

584
01:00:39.220 --> 01:00:40.680
You feel good. huh?

585
01:00:41.931 --> 01:00:44.100
Maybe you sing
a little song. eh?

586
01:00:45.226 --> 01:00:46.894
I will join you.

587
01:00:47.395 --> 01:00:50.231
We can sing together how
you saved the grateful chinos.

588
01:00:50.314 --> 01:00:52.733
You saw what happened
out there and that's what you say?

589
01:00:52.859 --> 01:00:53.943
I see black powder.

590
01:00:55.778 --> 01:00:57.071
I see a man
forget his friends.

591
01:00:57.738 --> 01:00:59.657
The black powder's
not going anywhere.

592
01:00:59.740 --> 01:01:01.826
What goes nowhere is you.

593
01:01:05.621 --> 01:01:07.915
You'll never get
what you want from this.

594
01:01:08.916 --> 01:01:11.377
You think they see you
as some kind of hero?

595
01:01:11.752 --> 01:01:13.588
A man of virtue?

596
01:01:14.338 --> 01:01:16.507
Maybe you can fool them.

597
01:01:16.591 --> 01:01:18.551
but I know what you are.

598
01:01:19.594 --> 01:01:22.263
You know what you are.

599
01:01:23.139 --> 01:01:24.599
A thief.

600
01:01:25.183 --> 01:01:26.517
a liar.

601
01:01:28.811 --> 01:01:30.271
and a killer.

602
01:01:32.648 --> 01:01:35.318
And you can never undo
the things you have done.

603
01:01:35.902 --> 01:01:37.028
and you will
never be anything.

604
01:01:45.786 --> 01:01:47.455
Good to see you again.
<i>amigo.</i>

605
01:01:58.090 --> 01:01:59.300
Tao Tei movement!

606
01:01:59.383 --> 01:02:01.886
Tao Tei movement!

607
01:02:02.094 --> 01:02:03.596
All troops to the Wall!

608
01:02:03.679 --> 01:02:05.139
All troops to the Wall!

609
01:02:08.643 --> 01:02:10.394
- Nothing?
- No.

610
01:02:10.478 --> 01:02:11.729
How do you know
he won't betray us?

611
01:02:11.812 --> 01:02:12.939
I don't.

612
01:02:13.022 --> 01:02:14.774
They'll kill him. They'll kill him no matter what.

613
01:02:14.857 --> 01:02:16.817
The time they spend
killing him

614
01:02:17.944 --> 01:02:20.112
is time they are
not chasing us.

615
01:03:02.280 --> 01:03:05.324
Careful with that.
There's powder here.

616
01:03:17.545 --> 01:03:19.005
Tovar.

617
01:03:50.161 --> 01:03:51.579
General. it goes
all the way through.

618
01:03:51.829 --> 01:03:53.247
Tao Tei have
breached the Wall.

619
01:03:53.331 --> 01:03:54.749
They're smarter
than we thought.

620
01:03:55.416 --> 01:03:57.209
Summon my commanders
immediately!

621
01:03:57.293 --> 01:03:58.419
Yes. General.

622
01:04:18.356 --> 01:04:21.108
Have a look.
See if it's gone out.

623
01:04:21.442 --> 01:04:22.568
Is it safe?

624
01:04:22.735 --> 01:04:24.278
Of course it is.

625
01:04:53.099 --> 01:04:55.476
Shake it off. man.
To work.

626
01:04:58.813 --> 01:05:01.148
I thought
you said it was safe?

627
01:05:02.066 --> 01:05:03.651
We're in. aren't we?

628
01:05:15.496 --> 01:05:16.872
You're here.

629
01:05:17.498 --> 01:05:18.999
We've come
to our senses. eh?

630
01:05:19.667 --> 01:05:20.918
Ballard has
planned well.

631
01:05:21.001 --> 01:05:22.920
Getting out is easy.

632
01:05:23.003 --> 01:05:25.297
There's a gate.
20 miles west.

633
01:05:25.464 --> 01:05:27.341
We dodge
the hill tribes.

634
01:05:28.509 --> 01:05:29.510
We can make it.

635
01:05:30.845 --> 01:05:31.971
They need us here.

636
01:05:32.054 --> 01:05:33.848
They need more than us.

637
01:05:34.807 --> 01:05:36.142
These people are doomed.

638
01:05:36.267 --> 01:05:37.351
Don't be a fool.

639
01:05:37.435 --> 01:05:38.436
I've been a fool.

640
01:05:38.519 --> 01:05:40.229
I'm done with it.

641
01:05:40.813 --> 01:05:42.189
Brother. please.

642
01:05:43.315 --> 01:05:45.359
We've been fighting
for nothing.

643
01:05:46.193 --> 01:05:47.445
For greed.

644
01:05:48.028 --> 01:05:51.198
<i>Amigo.</i>
after all the blood.

645
01:05:51.282 --> 01:05:53.784
and cold. and pain.

646
01:05:53.909 --> 01:05:56.287
with this black powder
in our saddle bags.

647
01:05:56.370 --> 01:05:57.872
we win.

648
01:05:59.165 --> 01:06:00.374
You come with me.

649
01:06:02.168 --> 01:06:03.419
I can't do that now.

650
01:06:05.629 --> 01:06:06.714
Stay and fight.

651
01:06:08.090 --> 01:06:09.383
William...

652
01:06:13.888 --> 01:06:14.972
Think he's dead?

653
01:06:15.055 --> 01:06:17.099
It'd take a lot
more than that.

654
01:06:21.896 --> 01:06:23.564
All of the attacks
have been a diversion...

655
01:06:23.647 --> 01:06:25.608
while they dug this tunnel.

656
01:06:25.733 --> 01:06:27.526
They have breached the Wall.

657
01:06:27.610 --> 01:06:30.362
Once they reach the capital...

658
01:06:30.905 --> 01:06:32.448
nothing in the world
can stop them.

659
01:06:33.199 --> 01:06:34.700
At a full gallop...

660
01:06:35.326 --> 01:06:36.785
it's two days to the capital.

661
01:06:37.328 --> 01:06:38.954
There is no way
we can catch them.

662
01:06:39.371 --> 01:06:41.081
The wind is strong now.

663
01:06:41.665 --> 01:06:43.751
It blows from the north
all day tomorrow.

664
01:06:44.293 --> 01:06:46.462
We have to use the balloons.

665
01:06:46.921 --> 01:06:48.589
If it works.
how long to Bianliang?

666
01:06:48.797 --> 01:06:50.591
Six hours if the wind holds.

667
01:06:50.674 --> 01:06:51.800
If we make it alive.

668
01:06:53.052 --> 01:06:56.639
General...
none of the tests have worked.

669
01:06:58.224 --> 01:06:59.266
Get ready!

670
01:07:09.151 --> 01:07:10.402
Come on.

671
01:07:10.903 --> 01:07:11.946
Hyah.

672
01:08:00.494 --> 01:08:01.870
How did you capture it?

673
01:08:01.996 --> 01:08:03.247
Your Excellency...

674
01:08:03.330 --> 01:08:04.331
Your Excellency!

675
01:08:04.456 --> 01:08:06.041
It's the magnet!

676
01:08:06.667 --> 01:08:09.169
It keeps the beast
under control.

677
01:08:09.295 --> 01:08:10.838
This is the most
important discovery...

678
01:08:10.963 --> 01:08:13.465
in the history of the Tao Tei.

679
01:08:13.674 --> 01:08:16.385
We will investigate
immediately.

680
01:08:16.677 --> 01:08:18.178
Bring him here!

681
01:08:35.362 --> 01:08:38.157
{\an8}I tried to stop them...
You dare to speak to me?

682
01:08:40.200 --> 01:08:41.410
I didn't do this.

683
01:08:42.036 --> 01:08:44.997
And you came here
to trade.

684
01:08:45.164 --> 01:08:46.999
And you knew nothing
of black powder.

685
01:08:49.168 --> 01:08:51.629
What a fool
you must think I am.

686
01:08:51.712 --> 01:08:53.964
If I was with them.
why would I be here?

687
01:08:54.048 --> 01:08:55.215
I tried to stop them.

688
01:08:55.299 --> 01:08:56.592
Liar!

689
01:08:57.843 --> 01:08:59.219
You lie.

690
01:09:00.888 --> 01:09:02.973
Some part of you knows
that's not true.

691
01:09:03.057 --> 01:09:07.978
If I were not the General.
I would kill you myself.

692
01:09:10.105 --> 01:09:11.273
General!

693
01:09:15.653 --> 01:09:16.862
General.

694
01:09:17.738 --> 01:09:18.947
Speak up!

695
01:09:20.783 --> 01:09:22.660
I was there when it happened.

696
01:09:22.868 --> 01:09:24.578
I saw him try to stop them.

697
01:09:33.796 --> 01:09:35.255
Are you sure?

698
01:09:38.592 --> 01:09:40.886
If you're lying.
I'll have your head!

699
01:09:41.595 --> 01:09:44.598
I swear on my vow
to the Nameless Order!

700
01:09:58.612 --> 01:09:59.613
Lock him up.

701
01:09:59.738 --> 01:10:01.824
Send the cavalry.
Go after the two that got away.

702
01:10:01.949 --> 01:10:03.117
Yes. General.

703
01:10:27.182 --> 01:10:28.976
Which way.
left or right?

704
01:10:29.643 --> 01:10:32.396
Go up and take a look
from the high ground.

705
01:10:44.491 --> 01:10:45.951
Hyah!

706
01:10:47.286 --> 01:10:48.370
No!

707
01:10:48.954 --> 01:10:51.457
No! Bastard!

708
01:11:33.707 --> 01:11:35.751
- Keep it steady!
- Yes. General!

709
01:11:35.834 --> 01:11:36.835
Watch the powder!

710
01:12:12.788 --> 01:12:14.164
What happened?

711
01:12:17.209 --> 01:12:18.377
What happened?

712
01:12:18.502 --> 01:12:20.337
We have failed.

713
01:12:20.504 --> 01:12:22.923
The Tao Tei
are in the Kingdom.

714
01:12:23.507 --> 01:12:26.927
You are free to leave.
Take what you wish and go.

715
01:12:27.052 --> 01:12:29.096
This was the
General's final order.

716
01:12:29.221 --> 01:12:30.389
Where is she?

717
01:12:34.977 --> 01:12:36.395
To do what?

718
01:12:36.478 --> 01:12:37.604
To fight?

719
01:12:37.729 --> 01:12:39.022
Is there a chance?

720
01:12:39.147 --> 01:12:40.274
There's only one.

721
01:12:40.774 --> 01:12:42.776
Kill the Queen.

722
01:12:42.860 --> 01:12:45.028
Kill the Queen.
or we all die.

723
01:12:46.864 --> 01:12:47.948
Leave.

724
01:12:48.532 --> 01:12:50.617
Tell the world
what you have seen.

725
01:12:50.701 --> 01:12:52.870
and tell them
what is coming.

726
01:13:15.893 --> 01:13:17.519
I'll need my bow.

727
01:13:21.273 --> 01:13:23.817
If I'm to join you.
I'll need my bow.

728
01:13:29.781 --> 01:13:31.325
Strategist Wang!

729
01:13:31.992 --> 01:13:34.369
Please take me with you.

730
01:13:35.370 --> 01:13:37.414
He wishes
to join us.

731
01:13:59.603 --> 01:14:00.687
Distance is the key.

732
01:14:01.813 --> 01:14:04.524
The magnet is only effective
when close to the beast.

733
01:14:05.692 --> 01:14:06.693
Therefore...

734
01:14:07.444 --> 01:14:09.529
the effect weakens
as it gets further away.

735
01:14:10.113 --> 01:14:12.199
You see I have it
under complete control.

736
01:14:16.078 --> 01:14:17.120
Write down nine feet.

737
01:15:31.903 --> 01:15:32.946
No.

738
01:15:33.030 --> 01:15:34.031
No.

739
01:15:38.702 --> 01:15:39.703
No.

740
01:15:44.583 --> 01:15:45.584
No.

741
01:15:47.127 --> 01:15:50.130
No. don't throw
that thing near fire!

742
01:16:06.104 --> 01:16:07.939
Steer to the rear
of the palace.

743
01:17:09.376 --> 01:17:10.752
Above you!

744
01:17:19.553 --> 01:17:20.554
Light a grenade!

745
01:17:20.679 --> 01:17:21.763
Yes. sir!

746
01:17:24.975 --> 01:17:26.560
Behind you!

747
01:17:39.156 --> 01:17:40.740
I set you free.

748
01:17:41.741 --> 01:17:43.076
And here I am.

749
01:17:44.786 --> 01:17:45.912
There's the Queen!

750
01:17:50.876 --> 01:17:53.295
They will not attack
while the Queen is feeding.

751
01:17:53.420 --> 01:17:55.338
We have a chance!

752
01:17:55.422 --> 01:17:56.506
Hold on!

753
01:18:11.062 --> 01:18:12.689
State your purpose!

754
01:18:27.579 --> 01:18:28.788
General Lin Mae
of the Nameless Order.

755
01:18:28.872 --> 01:18:29.956
At your service!

756
01:18:38.381 --> 01:18:39.716
What took you so long?

757
01:18:40.300 --> 01:18:42.802
The Tao Tei have
overrun the city!

758
01:18:42.928 --> 01:18:46.556
Thousands of soldiers
and innocents are dead.

759
01:18:46.640 --> 01:18:48.308
You're too late!

760
01:18:48.433 --> 01:18:50.560
Where is the captured Tao Tei?

761
01:18:50.644 --> 01:18:51.853
In the dungeon!

762
01:18:51.978 --> 01:18:53.313
We need it to kill the Queen.

763
01:18:53.438 --> 01:18:55.440
Once she is dead.
the Tao Tei cannot function.

764
01:18:55.649 --> 01:18:58.235
Without her signal.
their whole army will freeze.

765
01:19:18.505 --> 01:19:20.340
There is
an underground canal here.

766
01:19:20.507 --> 01:19:22.342
Has it been breached?

767
01:19:22.425 --> 01:19:23.927
The Tao Tei should
all be above ground.

768
01:19:24.636 --> 01:19:25.845
And the one we captured?

769
01:19:26.346 --> 01:19:27.347
<i>We load it up.</i>

770
01:19:28.473 --> 01:19:29.808
<i>We feed it.</i>

771
01:19:29.891 --> 01:19:31.851
<i>And it will return
to its Queen.</i>

772
01:19:32.060 --> 01:19:33.019
Good.

773
01:20:42.255 --> 01:20:45.258
You'll have one hell of a scar. but you'll live.

774
01:20:45.342 --> 01:20:46.343
He says you will live.

775
01:20:47.719 --> 01:20:49.387
We'll come back for him.

776
01:21:07.405 --> 01:21:08.865
They've broken through!

777
01:22:31.364 --> 01:22:33.992
Patience. William.

778
01:22:50.967 --> 01:22:54.053
And it will go to the Queen when it's done?

779
01:22:54.304 --> 01:22:55.513
It should.

780
01:22:58.057 --> 01:22:59.100
It will.

781
01:23:11.070 --> 01:23:12.071
Let it in.

782
01:23:36.137 --> 01:23:37.430
I can get a shot
from above.

783
01:23:42.477 --> 01:23:44.771
Go! I'll hold them back.

784
01:24:07.794 --> 01:24:09.295
Wait. Not yet.

785
01:24:17.887 --> 01:24:18.972
Hit.

786
01:24:28.147 --> 01:24:29.107
Go higher.

787
01:24:29.190 --> 01:24:30.650
I'll get
a better shot.

788
01:24:43.955 --> 01:24:44.956
General!

789
01:24:45.039 --> 01:24:46.332
It's up to you now!

790
01:25:39.218 --> 01:25:40.845
We have one black powder weapon left.

791
01:25:40.928 --> 01:25:42.388
Give me the spear.

792
01:25:44.557 --> 01:25:46.017
I've trained for this my whole life.

793
01:25:48.186 --> 01:25:49.437
Trust.

794
01:25:53.066 --> 01:25:54.192
I'll get you the shot.

795
01:26:40.321 --> 01:26:41.614
I've got you.

796
01:27:59.525 --> 01:28:01.611
So. how's life
without me?

797
01:28:02.862 --> 01:28:04.280
A little slow.

798
01:28:07.533 --> 01:28:09.160
You're a hero after all.

799
01:28:09.702 --> 01:28:10.953
Well. it looks that way.

800
01:28:11.037 --> 01:28:13.372
You seem pleased
with yourself.

801
01:28:13.456 --> 01:28:15.875
And what are they giving you
for all of your troubles?

802
01:28:16.042 --> 01:28:17.043
A bag of gold?

803
01:28:17.627 --> 01:28:19.796
A victory parade
along the top of the Wall?

804
01:28:20.379 --> 01:28:22.298
All the black powder
I can carry.

805
01:28:22.882 --> 01:28:25.593
And a cavalry escort
to get me home safely.

806
01:28:26.719 --> 01:28:28.054
Well. congratulations.

807
01:28:28.137 --> 01:28:29.972
Thank you.

808
01:28:30.056 --> 01:28:33.351
So what is this? You're here to rub my nose in it?

809
01:28:33.559 --> 01:28:34.977
Well. would you
blame me?

810
01:28:35.061 --> 01:28:37.438
The last time I saw you.
you left me for dead.

811
01:28:37.563 --> 01:28:39.482
And the time before that.
I saved your life.

812
01:28:39.565 --> 01:28:40.900
True.

813
01:28:43.236 --> 01:28:45.822
You know. the Emperor
gave me a choice.

814
01:28:45.905 --> 01:28:48.115
I could take
the black powder.

815
01:28:48.282 --> 01:28:50.618
or I could take you.

816
01:28:52.453 --> 01:28:54.413
Please tell me
you chose the powder?

817
01:29:01.671 --> 01:29:03.381
I don't even
know you anymore.

818
01:29:06.092 --> 01:29:07.718
The horses are
saddled and waiting.

819
01:29:07.802 --> 01:29:10.096
Best we ride
before nightfall.

820
01:29:15.601 --> 01:29:17.270
I'll be inside.

821
01:29:17.353 --> 01:29:19.230
Don't leave
without me.

822
01:29:29.949 --> 01:29:31.117
I came to say goodbye.

823
01:29:33.452 --> 01:29:36.706
I understand congratulations are in order.

824
01:29:36.873 --> 01:29:39.125
General of the northwest territory.

825
01:29:39.292 --> 01:29:40.960
That's quite
an honor.

826
01:29:43.462 --> 01:29:45.590
Seems you've made
your choice.

827
01:29:45.715 --> 01:29:46.799
Him?

828
01:29:46.966 --> 01:29:49.844
Believe me. I'm already thinking
about trading him back for the powder.

829
01:29:50.011 --> 01:29:51.971
I heard that.

830
01:29:57.643 --> 01:30:00.771
Perhaps we were
both wrong.

831
01:30:01.314 --> 01:30:03.983
We are more similar
than I thought.

832
01:30:09.655 --> 01:30:11.365
Thank you. General.

833
01:30:37.308 --> 01:30:39.352
Are you sure you don't
want to go back?

834
01:30:40.019 --> 01:30:41.020
Of course I do.

835
01:30:42.188 --> 01:30:44.690
I just don't trust you to make it out of here alone.
